[{"index": 0, "text": "How about maybe a little phrase or something, something in French that I could say?", "start": 0.0, "end": 3.271, "zh": "能不能教我一个法语的小短语或者什么的，我可以说说看？", "zh_hant": "能不能教我一個法語的小短語或者什麼的，我可以說說看？"}, {"index": 1, "text": "Okay, I'll teach you something that I learned recently.", "start": 3.652, "end": 6.673, "zh": "好啊，我教你个我最近学到的东西。", "zh_hant": "好啊，我教你個我最近學到的東西。"}, {"index": 2, "text": "So they have, like, their slang is all inverting words.", "start": 7.133, "end": 11.334, "zh": "他们的俚语好像都是把词倒过来说的。", "zh_hant": "他們的俚語好像都是把詞倒過來說的。"}, {"index": 3, "text": "Oh.", "start": 11.735, "end": 12.535, "zh": "哦。", "zh_hant": "哦。"}, {"index": 4, "text": "And someone taught me once that, like, to know a language, you have to know how the pronunciation.", "start": 12.135, "end": 17.337, "zh": "有人跟我说过，要真正了解一门语言，你得知道发音怎么发。", "zh_hant": "有人跟我說過，要真正瞭解一門語言，你得知道發音怎麼發。"}, {"index": 5, "text": "You have to know how they say, um, which for the French is, uh, uh.", "start": 17.197, "end": 20.698, "zh": "你得知道他们怎么发音，对法语来说就是，呃，呃。", "zh_hant": "你得知道他們怎麼發音，對法語來說就是，呃，呃。"}, {"index": 6, "text": "So, like, the whole, like, sound of the language is, uh.", "start": 21.859, "end": 24.68, "zh": "就是那种，整个语言的腔调，呃。", "zh_hant": "就是那種，整個語言的腔調，呃。"}, {"index": 7, "text": "You got to do it one more time.", "start": 24.28, "end": 25.82, "zh": "你得再来一遍。", "zh_hant": "你得再來一遍。"}, {"index": 8, "text": "Uh.", "start": 27.101, "end": 27.781, "zh": "呃。", "zh_hant": "呃。"}, {"index": 9, "text": "like with their thing.", "start": 27.981, "end": 29.121, "zh": "就带着他们那种感觉。", "zh_hant": "就帶著他們那種感覺。"}, {"index": 10, "text": "So, okay, this phrase is, c 'est trop chelou.", "start": 30.002, "end": 33.863, "zh": "好，这句话是，c'est trop chelou。", "zh_hant": "好，這句話是，c'est trop chelou。"}, {"index": 11, "text": "Oh, c 'est trop.", "start": 33.463, "end": 35.484, "zh": "哦，c'est trop。", "zh_hant": "哦，c'est trop。"}, {"index": 12, "text": "C 'est trop.", "start": 35.084, "end": 36.224, "zh": "C'est trop。", "zh_hant": "C'est trop。"}, {"index": 13, "text": "C 'est trop.", "start": 35.824, "end": 36.804, "zh": "C'est trop。", "zh_hant": "C'est trop。"}, {"index": 14, "text": "Chelou.", "start": 36.585, "end": 37.465, "zh": "Chelou。", "zh_hant": "Chelou。"}, {"index": 15, "text": "Chelou.", "start": 37.525, "end": 38.365, "zh": "Chelou。", "zh_hant": "Chelou。"}, {"index": 16, "text": "Trop chelou.", "start": 37.985, "end": 39.025, "zh": "Trop chelou。", "zh_hant": "Trop chelou。"}, {"index": 17, "text": "C 'est trop chelou.", "start": 38.745, "end": 39.986, "zh": "C'est trop chelou。", "zh_hant": "C'est trop chelou。"}, {"index": 18, "text": "Exactly.", "start": 39.886, "end": 41.746, "zh": "没错。", "zh_hant": "沒錯。"}, {"index": 19, "text": "It means too shady.", "start": 41.346, "end": 42.627, "zh": "意思是太可疑了。", "zh_hant": "意思是太可疑了。"}, {"index": 20, "text": "It's shady.", "start": 42.247, "end": 44.527, "zh": "就是很鬼祟、很不对劲。", "zh_hant": "就是很鬼祟、很不對勁。"}, {"index": 21, "text": "C 'est trop chelou.", "start": 45.488, "end": 47.309, "zh": "C'est trop chelou。", "zh_hant": "C'est trop chelou。"}, {"index": 22, "text": "C 'est trop chelou.", "start": 46.969, "end": 48.009, "zh": "C'est trop chelou。", "zh_hant": "C'est trop chelou。"}, {"index": 23, "text": "C 'est trop chelou.", "start": 47.609, "end": 49.049, "zh": "C'est trop chelou。", "zh_hant": "C'est trop chelou。"}, {"index": 24, "text": "Euh.", "start": 48.649, "end": 49.229, "zh": "呃。", "zh_hant": "呃。"}]